      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "A systematic mesh convergence study was performed on the screw-rod interface region and the vertebral body surrogate. Richardson extrapolation was applied; discretization error in peak von Mises stress is estimated at less than 3%, satisfying gradation 3."
    },
