      "rationale": "Testing was performed under a single quasi-static loading rate in ambient conditions. The ASME V&V 40 assessment identifies this as below the required gradation because dynamic or cyclic loading conditions relevant to in vivo use were not included in the validation experiments. This represents an acknowledged gap."
