      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "The validation activities replicate the ASTM F1717 test configuration in geometry, loading, and boundary conditions. The physical test is the regulatory benchmark for the intended use, confirming high relevance at gradation 3."
