    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/nagaraja-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation level for model risk level 3. The single shortfall in Test conditions (gradation 2 achieved versus 3 required) is acknowledged; the assessment team determined that the quasi-static loading condition is the primary regulatory use case and that the overall evidence base is sufficient to support an Accepted decision for the intended submission. The model has been applied in clinical research contexts and the evidence package is considered adequate for the declared scope under the Minimal profile.",
